- **`.gitignore`** — All required patterns present (logs/, reviews/, checkpoints/, .env, __pycache__/, .venv/, *.pyc via *.py[cod], .mypy_cache/, .ruff_cache/)
- **`Dockerfile`** — Uses `python:3.13-slim` base image, exposes port 8000, installs deps, copies src, runs uvicorn
- **`docker-compose.yml`** — Service `agent`, port 8000 mapping, env_file .env, checkpoints volume
- **`scripts/local_ci.sh`** — Correct sequence (ruff check → ruff format --check → mypy → pytest), executable permissions, `set -euo pipefail`
- **`tests/test_scaffold.py`** — Covers all 5 acceptance criteria with parametrized tests
- **Coding standards compliance** — `from __future__ import annotations` used, Google-style docstrings, proper import ordering
